dt-option.default:
        The default value for the `-init searchPanes.dataLength` paramater is `30`. Meaning that as standard after 30 characters the cell will cut off the end and append '...'.


        As standard, SearchPanes will be displayed with the cells which have a length greater than 30 characters as the first 30 characters postfixed by '...'.

		This is useful as it prevents the cells becoming mishapen and overpopulated.





 $('#example').DataTable( {
        searchPanes:{
            dataLength: 15,
        },    
    });
